aka: Island – Reise zum Ursprung der Erde
trans_title: Island – Reise zum Ursprung der Erde
introduction: Dive into the heart of a unique expedition, between exceptional landscapes, legendary lands and human adventure.Our planet is home to fascinating natural monuments, such as the Icelandic volcanoes , which testify to the beauty and power of nature. These exceptional landscapes are witnesses to the telluric forces and biological processes that have shaped the Earth for billions of years.Production: ARTE, CNC, Grand Angle Productions, RSI
